&lt;li&gt;Partner with engineering and compliance teams to build privacy-enhancing systems and infrastructure, on topics including vendor due diligence, third party privacy and security assessments, governance, risk and compliance, data use, and privacy and security incident response&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide pragmatic, actionable, and globally-oriented advice to minimize legal risks while advancing business goals and objectives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with stakeholders to help develop, improve, and enforce Discord’s data security policies, standards, and practices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help ensure Discord’s data processing globally complies with all applicable privacy laws, including the EU General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and state and federal consumer protection and privacy laws&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as one of the company’s experts on issues related to privacy, ML development, and more&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with colleagues in Legal on privacy issues that arise in the development of new products and technologies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead internal projects, process development, and training to empower the business and your colleagues&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you should have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;JD from an accredited law school&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Admission to the California Bar or eligible to register as in-house counsel with the California Bar&lt;/li&gt;
